1328	/// `CompactBoringNodes`) and every non-System ellipse (missing / action / last)
1329	/// map ALL their prem/conc keys to the bare node id (no port, Dot.hs:303-304).
1330	/// `node_map` holds only System nodes, so an id absent from it is a non-System
